sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant OS as Order Service
    participant EB as Event Bus
    participant IS as Inventory Service
    participant PS as Payment Service
    participant SS as Shipping Service
    participant NS as Notification Service
    
    rect rgb(200, 230, 201)
    Note over User,OS: 1. ORDER PLACED
    User->>OS: Place Order
    OS->>EB: Publish: Order Placed Event
    Note right of EB: {orderId, userId, items}
    end
    
    rect rgb(187, 222, 251)
    Note over EB,PS: 2. PARALLEL PROCESSING
    EB->>IS: Order Placed Event
    EB->>PS: Order Placed Event
    EB->>NS: Order Placed Event
    
    par Inventory Update
        IS->>IS: Check & Update Stock
        IS->>EB: Publish: Inventory Updated
    and Payment Processing
        PS->>PS: Process Payment
        PS->>EB: Publish: Payment Processed
    and User Notification
        NS->>User: Send: Order Placed Notification
        NS->>EB: Publish: Notification Sent
    end
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 245, 157)
    Note over OS,EB: 3. ORDER CONFIRMATION
    EB->>OS: Inventory Updated Event
    EB->>OS: Payment Processed Event
    OS->>OS: Validate Both Events
    OS->>EB: Publish: Order Confirmed
    end
    
    rect rgb(206, 147, 216)
    Note over EB,SS: 4. SHIPPING SCHEDULED
    EB->>SS: Order Confirmed Event
    SS->>SS: Schedule Shipping
    SS->>EB: Publish: Shipping Scheduled
    EB->>NS: Shipping Scheduled Event
    NS->>User: Send: Shipping Details
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 204, 188)
    Note over User,NS: 5. PROCESS COMPLETE
    NS->>User: Send: Order Complete Notification
    end